{"tid":1098691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲女殺5歲弟剁GG　一口吞下採陽補陰","createTime":"2019-04-09T08:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T03:59:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b83557430f9560c056968c6ad34cd20ff9647b71","tid":1098691,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"巴西一名女子疑似誤信邪教，在同好慫恿下殺了5歲的弟弟，並把他分屍剁GG吞下肚。<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，巴西聖保羅18歲少女卡琳娜‧羅克（Karina Roque），承認殺了5歲的弟弟以後吃下他的陰莖，警方調查後發現卡琳娜殺死弟弟疑似跟黑魔法疑似有關，因為屍體是在報蠟燭包圍的地板上發現。<br />\n警方指出，4日時，卡琳娜母親出門購物，幾個小時回家後發現家門上鎖，最後在親戚幫忙下破門而入，結果看到兒子慘遭分屍當場昏倒，而陷入瘋狂狀態的卡琳娜立即逃走，逃走圖中還丟石頭攻擊叔叔、咬了家裡養的狗。卡琳娜被逮後坦承，她假裝和弟弟玩遊戲，引誘弟弟到她的防煙，然後用枕頭把弟弟用窒息。<br />\n初步檢查顯示，弟弟身體被殘忍分屍，而案發現場發現被燒毀的手機、記憶卡、小刀以及些許的大麻，調查人員指出，卡琳娜銷毀手機可能是要隱藏跟其他人聯絡的證據。目前警方將安排卡琳娜進行毒品測試，手機跟記憶卡也將送去相關單位分析。5日時家屬已經把弟弟下葬，家屬不願意對該起事件發表意見。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190409/640_9e82581d22a6c6dc6fe57dda16b639fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190409%2F640_9e82581d22a6c6dc6fe57dda16b639fb.jpg&h=7be6b720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190409/640_fdeeff71e083998110912ab35a441cff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190409%2F640_fdeeff71e083998110912ab35a441cff.jpg&h=796c4b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190409/640_bccdc76950f9a8c4bffeaa682968ed81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190409%2F640_bccdc76950f9a8c4bffeaa682968ed81.jpg&h=f1cf1a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190409/640_11146aeafe8267ec61770277df0e293a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190409%2F640_11146aeafe8267ec61770277df0e293a.jpg&h=9599ebd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190409/1547620/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190409%2F1547620%2F&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=26a23603\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190409%2F1547620%2F&h=5b03b249\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190409/1547620/</a>"},{"pid":"4c81009f8b440cb11d75c5ee63581a0c8b3f7fba","tid":1098691,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"逃走圖中還丟石頭攻擊叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e279665ceea3312b3118b4c891275850d21bc0","tid":1098691,"uid":157193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afda8c8753577f8054098964ca909f315110d0e","tid":1098691,"uid":229161,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"睇d圖 你話佢四十我都信"},{"pid":"8dbeed08e581794ffc7a0a1b742523b10163567c","tid":1098691,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"好吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b1451939dbdea27485e96b31d7601044752ee7","tid":1098691,"uid":37661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4c81009f8b440cb11d75c5ee63581a0c8b3f7fba","tid":1098691,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"逃走圖中還丟石頭攻擊叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"引誘弟弟到她的防煙<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢中文嚟架"},{"pid":"6e7d9ae5190b911f93313bf658599e45d7030cb7","tid":1098691,"uid